text:
RT @NYDailyNews: Entering the world of "exponentially" growing QAnon group is like stumbling into a fringe fantasyland embracing every crackpot conspiracy theory of the last two decades.

Trump tweeted about QAnon: “I understand they like me very much, which I appreciate.”

name: NYDailyNews
text:
A fight between 2 homeless men turned deadly after one was shoved into a wall on a Brooklyn street Sunday afternoon.

The victim was battling a 43-year-old man in Borough Park, got shoved and fell, cops said.
https://t.co/aVMBAh0FhM

name: NYDailyNews
text:
Hall of Famer Lou Brock — one of baseball’s signature leadoff hitters and base stealers who helped the Cardinals win 3 pennants and two World Series titles — has died at 81.

The Cardinals and Cubs also observed a moment of silence.
